@startuml UC9_EditCourseContent
title UC9 - Edit Course Content
!include https://raw.githubusercontent.com/fredoslav2004/MinimalThemePUML/refs/heads/main/minimal-theme.puml

actor Teacher
participant System

Teacher -> System: Open own courses
System --> Teacher: Retrieve courses assigned to teacher
Teacher -> System: Select course to edit
System --> Teacher: Provide course content
alt Add New Learning Step
    Teacher -> System: Add new learning step
    System -> System: Create new step
    System --> Teacher: Show the new step
else Edit Existing Learning Step
    Teacher -> System: Select learning step to edit
    System --> Teacher: Provide current step content
    Teacher -> System: Edit learning step, save changes
    System -> System: Update step content
    System --> Teacher: Confirm step update
end
@enduml
